Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.40,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What the...? That's nothing but simple luck.}Hả...? Cái này hoàn toàn do may mắn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:21.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Perfect! I will start winning now.}Quá tuyệt! Mình sẽ bắt đầu thắng lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:27.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Why? Because I've memorized the birthdays of everyone in my fan club!}Tại sao? Vì mình nhớ ngày thắng năm sinh từng người trong fanclub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna lose this time!}Lần này tao sẽ thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:33.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ticket sales were restricted to fan club members only.}Vé này chỉ bán cho thành viên fanclub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And I also know the birthdays of the student council members.}Và mình cũng biết ngày tháng năm sinh thành viên Hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.90,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're going down, Jabami Yumeko!}Mày thua rồi, Jabami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:45.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{All in all, this was probably the only game I could win, right?}Quả nhiên chỉ có trò này là tớ có thể thắng thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.86,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The tens on the black dice is 3!}Là số 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.98,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I believed that until now.}Tớ đã xác nhận được một chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:59.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There was no way for me to win all those games.}Thực sự tớ không thể nào thắng những trò này.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But somehow I did it.}Nhưng không biết tại sao lại thắng?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:07.70,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Because you chose to make this gambling match more exciting.}Tức là cậu đã chọn như thế để trò chơi thêm phần thú vị.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.34,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The first-class idol through and through.}Quả là idol nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.14,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thanks to you, I've got a chance to win this too.}Nhờ cậu tớ đã có cơ hội thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Now then...}Nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.84,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Shall we gamble?}Cờ bạc điên cuồng nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:25.16,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And we have thirty... one!\NNumber thirty-one!}Là số 31...Số 31!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ugh. Me? Really?}Vãi...Mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{W-W-Who the hell are you?}M-M-Mày là con nào?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.58,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Mary-san! Right on target!}A Mary! Đúng rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:44.14,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No way! Is she controlling her rolls somehow?}Không lẽ...nó kiểm soát được xúc xắc?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And why are there other people mixed in with the fan club members?}Và tại sao lại có mấy đứa đó trong fanclub?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.78,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Was it a mistake? Or just luck?}Nhầm lẫn? Hay do may mắn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's no way it could be!}Không thể nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:56.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Most likely Yumeko planned all of it.\NAnd it's going her way!}Chắc chắn Yumeko đã tính hết. Và nó đang thắng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:00.28,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko saw right through me!}Yumeko đã nhìn ra ngay từ đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She rolled this "Fan appreciation" game on purpose.}Và chọn ngay trò này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.86,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And she picked her friend from the audience.}Sau đó chọn ra bạn của mình từ ghế khán giả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{How did she do all that?}Tại sao nó có thể làm được?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's only one way!}Chỉ có một khả năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:17.54,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's spent a few minutes reading the stage planner earlier,\Nand that's all she needed to come up with a winning strategy!}Nó dành vài phút đọc qua chương trình và lên kế hoạch này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:22.16,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemite-san. I know what's on your mind.}Yumemite, tớ biết cậu đang cảm thấy gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.54,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Doubt, anger, desperation...}Nghi ngờ, tức giận, tuyệt vọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:30.90,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I know how it feels. You probably want to scream now.}Ngay bây giờ cậu rất muốn hét lên nhỉ? Hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:37.34,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But please, save it for later!\NAt least until this gamble is over! Pretty please.}Nhưng hãy để sau trò này nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:43.92,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Alright. It's time to guess number 31's birth month.}Rồi. Vậy tháng sinh của người đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.68,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I have no idea what her birthday is...}Mình có biết nó là con quái nào đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemite-san, you're spacing out.}Yumemite, mắt cậu đang dãn ra đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.52,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Did she just wrote a "6"?}Nó vừa viết số 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The answer is June!}Câu trả lời là Tháng 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No, wait.}Không, khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Maybe she's not that dumb.}Con này mà ngu thế sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.56,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It can't be a mistake.}Không thể có chuyện nhầm lẫn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She made it obvious on purpose.}Nó làm có mục đích.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But why?}Nhưng tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's a chance she wrote a "9"!}Có khả năng là 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:30.28,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's trying to force me into writing "6"!}Nó cố tình dụ mình viết 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:40.36,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{This might a trap as well.\NBut if she did that on purpose, it'd be safer for her to not give me any info at all.}Có thể là bẫy. Nhưng tại sao nó lại cố ý làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The correct answer is September!}Câu trả lời là tháng 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{No mistake about it!}Chắc chắn là thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The answers are in!}Câu trả lời đã được viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.56,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Are you ready?}Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Isn't this exciting, Yumemite-san?}Vui thật đó, Yumemite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:58.98,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{A single card will decide that one of our lives is over.}Vì cuộc đời của một con người được quyết định qua thẻ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.14,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's scary. Don't say such horrible things.}Cậu đừng nó mấy thứ đáng sợ đó chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:09.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And now, girls...\NShow us your answers!}Và giờ...hãy cho xem câu trả lời nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{June?}Tháng 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.12,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Did I overthink it?}Mình suy luận ngu rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:25.16,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Or did she know that's what I'll do?}Hay cô ta đọc ra điều đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So, number 31, can you tell us your birthday?}Rồi số 31, tháng sinh là?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.38,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's the eight of March.}Ngày 8 tháng 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.38,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.6,82.4)}??:D??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:38.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's it! Yumeko-chan's the closest!\NShe wins the game!}Yumeko thắng trò này!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And of course your pick is...?}Và dĩ nhiên vị trí sẽ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.78,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Top one, please.}Phía trên ở giữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.10,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's a three in a row!}Đã hoàn thành!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.48,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko-chan is the champion!}Yumeko là nhà vô địch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumemi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:59.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{W-Why?}T-Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't understand what were you thinking.}Tao không hiểu mày nghĩ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{March? Seriously?}Tháng 3? Đùa nhau à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So why did you write a "6" then?}Thế mắc gì mày viết 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You could've lost it all if I guessed closer!}Mày sẽ thua nếu tao viết số nhỏ hơn 6 đấy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, I don't really know Mary-san's birthday...}Thì tớ có biết Mary sinh tháng nào đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:24.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I only worried about the two of us writing identical numbers.}Tớ chỉ lo khi cậu viết số giống với mình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:29.34,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{A tie is basically a guarantee that I lose.\NSo that's boring.}Tớ phải đảm bảo điều đó không xảy ra. Và nó cũng chán nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{As long as I'm able to gamble, that's fine with me.}Chỉ cần chơi bạc thú vị là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, as long as it's not a tie.} Cũng may là tớ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:40.42,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{So I lost because I had bad luck?}Vậy tôi thua chỉ vì thiếu may mắn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:45.56,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's all it takes.}Thế chả phải tốt sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{The absurdity of being helpless to decide your own fate...}Sự bất lực khi để số phận quyết định...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:53.04,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's the essence of gambling.}Đó mới là bản chất của cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.94,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It was really fun!}Tớ vui lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And now...}Giờ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.08,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I assume you're ready to pay up?}Trả tiền thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:17.30,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We will pay you 50 million yen, of course.\NAnd even more if you'd like but...}Bọn tôi sẽ trả 50 triệu yên. Và nhiều hơn nếu cô muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Will you promise not to release that audio recording to the public?}Nhưng xin đừng công bố thứ đó ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.70,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If it gets out...}Nếu chuyện đó xảy ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemi's future will be destroyed.}Tương lai của Yumemi sẽ bị phá nát.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemite-san, is that what you want too?}Yumemite, cậu cũng muốn thế chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.60,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Play the tape.}Phát nó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.20,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemi... What are you doing?}C-Cậu định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.24,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{To make my dream come true I needed luck.}Để giấc mơ thành hiện thực, tớ phải có may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:50.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{If luck fails me at a time like this, \Nthere's no way I'd make it come true.}Nếu không qua được lần này, chắc chắn sẽ không thể đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.22,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's okay.}Không sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.98,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're taking it well.}Có quyết tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.44,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.64,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{What's up with Yumemi-chan?}Yumemi sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.96,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Are they arguing?}Họ đang tranh luận à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:13.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemi, are you really sure?}Yumemi, cậu chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.26,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't care if they look gross or whatever.}Tôi không quan tâm chúng kinh tởm ra sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.62,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It just means that they spend their cash on me instead of their looks.}Chỉ là chúng đã sử dụng tiền để mua sản phẩm của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:32.98,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{But what's up with those dances during my shows?}Nhưng nhảy múa trong buổi diễn của tôi là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.52,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Listen to my songs instead of dancing!}Nghe bài hát của tôi đi chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.56,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Why the hell do they try harder than me on stage?}Tại sao bọn mày lại cố gắng hơn cả tao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:43.54,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And don't go grabbing and shaking my hands with those greasy, sweaty palms of yours!\NIt's gross!}Và đừng có bắt tay tao với toàn mồ hôi thế chứ! Thật kinh tởm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.80,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hey... That voice... Yumemi-chan?}Này...giọng của...Yumemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.70,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's not her usual self at all...}Khác hoàn toàn với lúc diễn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.16,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Listen, everyone.}Nghe đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.74,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That is indeed my voice.}Đó là giọng của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's how I really feel.}Cảm xúc thực sự của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.56,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{That was real me.}Bản chất của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.06,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I apologize for deceiving you all this time.}Tôi rất xin lỗi vì đã giấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:12.76,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{And thank you for cheering me on this whole time.}Và cám ơn vì đã ủng hộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:25.02,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's over. My dream... My aspirations...\NEverything I've built as a pop-idol...}Kết thúc rồi...Giấc mơ...Khát vọng...Những ấp ủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.66,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's all over...}Tất cả đã chấm hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:31.10,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{There's no point in my life anymore.}Cuộc đời của mình chẳng còn ý nghĩa gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.82,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemi-chan, I love you!}Yumemi, anh thích em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.50,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumemi-chan, it doesn't matter what you think about us!}Anh không quan tâm em nghĩ gì về bọn anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.78,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We didn't fall in love with you because you acted nice to us!}Bọn anh thích em không phải vì điều đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:50.92,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{We loved you from the very beginning!}Ngay từ đầu bọn anh đã thích em rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:53.80,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{T-That's right!}Đ-Đúng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.30,HorribleSubs,,0,0,0,,{I still want to cheer you on, Yumemi-chan!}Tớ vẫn muốn ủng hộ Yumemi!
